item.title: About me
item.description: A picture of me out on a nightwalk. My cat Meatball, who I love very much. Hello! I'm Joshua Gilliland. I am 18 years old and majoring in Computer Enginnering at UCF. Cybersecurity is my biggest passion, and I particularly enjoy defensive-offensive competitions, CTF (Capture the Flag), reverse engineering, and embedded security. I love programming, particularly in C and C++. I am proficient in Python and Bash scripting, and I'm currently expanding my skills by learning Rust.
